Just a small guide, how to configure internal server parameters.

This configuration will send a notice when recived a package
like:
Recived package: ( 14 14 00 00 03 00 05 05 01 00 86 05 )

spb_iparam = (
  {
    id = 5;
    type = 1;
    notify_msg = "Motion detected at the backside.";
    notify_pri = 3;
  },{
  // Second param
  } );